    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh i've heard about serotonin syndrome but i feel like my doctor would've mentioned if it was a huge deal. i've read online that because st johns wort is just a herb it's mostly just extra support. i only wanted to take a small dose of it, like one pill a day, so wouldn't that be fine? i really dont want to deal with a doctor's appointment right now with all my exams.",
