      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what u mean but im a bit skeptical about how dangerous it actually is since i see people talking about taking supplements with meds all the time. if i just take it once in a while when i'm feeling really bad, or maybe just a really low dose, would that still be a big risk? it seems like a lot of warnings are just to be extra cautious and it shouldn't be that easy to get sick.",
